transcript.text: Hi everyone, welcome to on print shop.
In this video we will see the new features and enhancements of B2B module which we have included in version 613.
These are major upgrades for B2B.
First one is we have introduced logo upload interface, second corporate admin order section enhancement, then order approval listing enhancement.
Then we have introduced a new button that is that will be used for notification management and order due date recalculation.
And this time we have introduced A2 e-mail section for department size as well and the last one image validation in image block.
So let me explain all these features to you.
So very first thing logo, upload interface.
We often got complaints that admins were not able to change logo from their side and when it used to come for to corporate section it was confusing which logo will be used.
To resolve this concern we have introduced upload logo interface.
So to find this when you will go to store personalization then website themes you will find a new button website logos.
Once you click on that you will see user type.
By selecting user type you can change logo for that particular user type.
So let's just say I have selected dream Realtors here.
So I can upload upload site logo for dream Realtors, I can upload logo for e-mail, I can upload a different logo for mobiles.
I can upload a studio logo even I can upload favicon as well.
And for studio app also we have provided this logo button here.
If corporate main site is missing logo then corporate logo then retail logo will be referred.
So this is all about logo upload interface.
Now we have made few changes in order listing section as well for corporate.
Let me show you those changes by logging in one of these corporate.
Yes Sir.
If I click in, in dream Realtors, you will see on dashboard itself like you can see how many orders are pending for approval, how many approved orders are there.

So this is 1 change one enhancement that we have made on dashboard itself and when I go to list order section I you will see a small icon there and by clicking on that icon you can see the information of approver and status of that particular order.
So these two enhancements we have made in corporate listing page.
Next feature that we have introduced that is notification management control that you can find in corporate admin edit tab.
When you will go to corporates edit tab you will see a new button there.
Here we have provided manage e-mail notification.
We got different queries from our corporate admins like sometimes they want to receive emails and sometimes they don't.
To resolve this concern we have provided this button.
So if corporate users, one corporate users want to receive e-mail only then you do not need to take corporate admin.
But if you want to receive notifications about all these orders as an admin as well, that time you can take it and you will receive all these notifications.
Next feature is order due date recalculation for manager approval.
Till this time what used to happen?
Let's just say a corporate user has placed order today and he will see estimated delivery date as per store settings.
But now what system will do?
Once manager approve the order, system will recalculate order due date and it will show user a new estimated delivery time.
Next word next feature that we have introduced that is department wise to e-mail.
When you will go and create a department, you can put a department e-mail as well.
This e-mail can be used to receive all emails triggered for this specific department.
You can add multiple e-mail addresses as well.
You just need to separate them with a comma.
Next feature is image validation in image block.
Till this time what used to happen in PDF blocks If there is a block for image and customer used to skip that.
But in this new version, we have provided image validation.
So if this image validation is activated then users will not be able to skip that particular field.
They will have to put one image there.
So this was all about version 6.3 for corporate management module.

If any feature that you have that you were looking for and you could not find it, you can write back to us at support at on printshop.com and we will make sure that we will add this feature in our upcoming version.
Thank you for your time.
Thank you for this session.
Bye bye.
